@node "NIT" "Known issues and tips"  

  @{JCENTER}@{IMG "GUIDEDIR:files/32seonliner.png"}@{JLEFT}








  32se onliner does not save anything 
  When a new issue is online, old is gone!
  To save/preserv this you find it in RAM:32se-main/
  
  If you get enviroment error during/after DL then run Prefs/Locale 
  set and save 
  
  HiP, Play16 and Lha needs to be in path eg. in c: and WHDL installed
  if your not running this on AmigaOS 32se
  
  
  
  
  
  
